    {
      "id": "PopularPost239377",
      "post_content": "The simplest use I can think of for this one is to adapt your color hate spells (circles of protection, elemental blasts, etc.) to every situation, but I'm sure Johnnies out there would have more rewarding uses to put it to.  \nSee also the strictly better [Mind Bend](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Bend) which offers more flexibility, and [Glamerdye](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glamerdye) which costs ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol) more but is retraceable.",
      "posted_by": "Trygon_Predator",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost239377\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">The simplest use I can think of for this one is to adapt your color hate spells (circles of protection, elemental blasts, etc.) to every situation, but I'm sure Johnnies out there would have more rewarding uses to put it to.<br/>See also the strictly better <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Bend\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Bend\">Mind Bend</a> which offers more flexibility, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Glamerdye\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glamerdye\">Glamerdye</a> which costs <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/> more but is retraceable.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '239377'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy81247\">Trygon_Predator</span>\r\n                                (4/26/2012 8:49:34 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_posts