      "id": "PopularPost249114",
      "post_content": "@Trygon\\_Predator: [Mind Bend](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Bend) is totally not strictly better than this. I wouldn't even say it was abstractly better. [Sleight of Mind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleight of Mind) can target spells as well as permanents. [Mind Bend](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Bend) does have the basic land thing, though. They're simply different.  \n  \nEither way, they're both great. You can tell any color to [Chill](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chill).",
